      "message": "I\u0027ve confirmed that the caller handles it correctly, these are simply renamed overrides from AndroidPipe:\n\n    int onGuestRecv(AndroidPipeBuffer* buffers, int numBuffers) final {\n        return writeBuffers(buffers, numBuffers);\n    }\n\n    int onGuestSend(const AndroidPipeBuffer* buffers, int numBuffers) final {\n        return readBuffers(buffers, numBuffers);\n    }\n\nThere\u0027s also unittest coverage that validates this case, and I added a comment to AndroidPipe to indicate that pipe isn\u0027t valid after onGuestRecv/onGuestSend.  Let me know if you have any other suggestions.",
